   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n249_saint_guard-accepting-c" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>I wanted to console him,<BR> but the only thing I could do was to be beside him and listen to his memories about the sister.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n249_saint_guard-accepting-d" mid="12" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>He said his sister loved pretty things.<BR> So she used to pick up and collect anything pretty among men's objects.<BR>That ornament is one of those. Mandra had also brought a good few objects to her.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n249_saint_guard-accepting-e" mid="14" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>So that's the story….</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>One day his sister saw a pretty ornament near Saint Haven. She had planned to pick it up at night, but that day of all days, Mandra wasn't with her because of his appointment with a friend. She left in spite of the attempts to stop her, that it could be dangerous for her to go out alone, and then….</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-accepting-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n249_saint_guard-accepting-f" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171><FONT color=#2b2723>What's that?</FONT></FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>I think Mandra plans to bury all of his sister's keepsakes in her grave.<BR>
He said he would like to bury that ornament she wanted to have back then together. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n249_saint_guard-accepting-f" image="QN_Npc_Caraban_Atdin.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n249_saint_guard-accepting-g" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>If it's an ornament from a foreign land, that Pero might know about it.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$Royal Guard Roy$<BR>I don't know the exact name. I heard the description, but it seemed to be an ornament from a foreign land.<BR>
Perhaps an expert of those things might know something....</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
