   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-1-b" mid="72" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I would like to ask you something.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="71"><![CDATA[<html>$Dishonest Merchant Pero$<BR>Hoho don't be like that. I have finally prepared somethin for you… Let me see.<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Pero begins to rummage through a box on which it's written 'articles in stock')</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-1-c" mid="74" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Have you recently sold an ornament made of metal?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="73"><![CDATA[<html>$Dishonest Merchant Pero$<BR>What? You didn't come to buy something? Pht.<BR>
…Well, ask me then.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-1-d" mid="76" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#2b2723>Do you sell it?</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="75"><![CDATA[<html>$Dishonest Merchant Pero$<BR>Ornament? Ah… Not long ago, a hometown friend left me some pieces.<BR>So I had them hanging on the display stand as for decoration, but everyone would just look at them curiously and leave.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-1-d" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="400347" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-1-e" mid="78" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>A marble made of iron?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="77"><![CDATA[<html>$Dishonest Merchant Pero$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Pero's eyes sparkle)<BR></FONT>Are you going to buy it? Are you going to buy it? Sure~ That's my id... I mean, customer!<BR>
But the word 'free' is not in my dictionary. And this is a bit expensive. Though I can offer you a special barter.<BR>
Do you know something called <FONT color=#a82424>glass-iron marble</FONT>?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-1-e" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="400347" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-1-f" mid="80" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>That sounds like a cheap name.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="79"><![CDATA[<html>$Dishonest Merchant Pero$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Pero sighs)<BR></FONT>That's a cheap answer. If it's simply a marble made of iron, then I wouldn't have got it.<BR>It is hard as if made of iron, but its inside shines transparently and eternally, hence its name glass-iron marble.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-1-f" image="QW_71.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-2" mid="82" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Alright then.(That's the <FONT color=#a82424>Intruder's Forward Base </FONT>)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="81"><![CDATA[<html>$Dishonest Merchant Pero$<BR>Hm hm, anyway, if you bring me that glass-iron marble, I will give you that ornament.<BR> I heard it can be found at some kind of a base in a desert.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n277_bluff_dealers_pope-2" image="QW_71.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
